# Parametric Claim Trigger Logic

The parametric insurance mechanism automatically generates claims when disruption conditions are met.

![Trigger Logic](docs/parametric_trigger.png)

| Event | Condition |
|------|------|
| Heavy Rain | Rainfall > 80 mm |
| Heat Wave | Temperature > 42°C |
| Severe Pollution | AQI > 350 |
| Flood Alert | Government warning |

